## Prerequisites

- Go {{goVersion}} or higher
- Make (optional)

## Getting Started

### Install dependencies
```bash
go mod download
```

### Run the service
```bash
go run main.go
```

Or using Make:
```bash
make run
```

### Build
```bash
make build
```

### Test
```bash
make test
```

## API Endpoints

- `GET /health` - Health check
- `GET /api/v1/hello` - Example endpoint
{{#if enableMetrics}}
- `GET /metrics` - Prometheus metrics
{{/if}}

## Configuration

Environment variables:
- `PORT` - Server port (default: 8080)
- `GIN_MODE` - Gin mode (debug, release, test)

## Docker

Build image:
```bash
docker build -t {{projectName}} .
```

Run container:
```bash
docker run -p 8080:8080 {{projectName}}
```

